data.name: label8.Text
data.value:
-Main manu- 1) Take front mugshot 2) Take side mugshot 3) inmate information text box 4) start new mugshot process 5) Save mugshots 6) Open the brightness settings menu 7) Open the application settings Menu 8) open the Help menu
-Brightness settings menu- 9) Enable the buttons to change shutter speed and focal length 10) change shutter speed 11) change focal length 12) show shutter speed, focal length, and brightness(gain) data on screen 13) change brightness(gain) 14) close the brightness setting menu
-application settings menu- 15) change the file path to save mugshots. 16) change if you want to override mugshots each time or keep every mugshots taken. 17) change if you want to open the folder when saved mugshot 18) select the camera you want to use 19) if you have PTZ camera, select corresponding controller. if not, select "no contoller" 20) save settings changed.
